rows.label: tlk70000005_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Dad says you guys are going
somewhere really dangerous.

rows.label: tlk70000005_04_msg0002
rows.name:
He says you're going to take care of
something that only you'd know how
to deal with...

rows.label: tlk70000005_04_msg0003
rows.name:
Sounds tough... I'm sorry you guys have
to do stuff like that alone...

rows.label: tlk70000005_04_msg0004
rows.name:
But I mean, I'd feel bad if I left you
totally in the lurch. So I decided to
give you a good send off at least.

rows.label: tlk70000005_04_msg0005
rows.name:
Please come back safe and sound!
Me, Joey and all of us are looking
forward to seeing you again!
